author: sfgate.com
title: Horoscope for Thursday, 10/15/15 by Christopher Renstrom
text:
ARIES. (March 20 - April 19): Your hard work pay off. You'll make a positive impression with a superior who harbored serious doubts about you.
TAURUS. (April 20 - May 20): You've proven your dependability. Now it's time for others who questioned you to prove their worth and lasting power.
GEMINI. (May 21 - June 20): Don't get frustrated with that work-in-progress. You're in the process of mastering a situation that has thwarted you for far too long.
CANCER. (June 21 - July 21): You need to be in a loved one's corner. Expressing that you know he can get through this gives him the confidence to persevere and prevail.
LEO. (July 22 - Aug. 22): A financial solution won't be everything you hoped for but it's still better than the problem you started out with. And that's progress of a sorts.
VIRGO. (Aug. 23 - Sept. 22): There's something to be said for being too busy to obsess over details. Ironically this makes you more productive than you would have been with a more relaxed schedule.
LIBRA. (Sept. 23 - Oct. 22): The clause you're looking at has been subtly altered over time which means you'll have to reproduce earlier versions to correct the error.
SCORPIO. (Oct. 23 - Nov. 21): The Mars/Pluto trine signals a breakthrough for you. This will put you back on course to establishing the security that has eluded you for too long.
SAGITTARIUS. (Nov. 22 - Dec. 20): Remember that it's your indefatigable optimism that drives you forward to break with convention and to blaze a new trail.
CAPRICORN. (Dec. 21 - Jan. 19): Your goal is in reach so don't push more than you have to. Let developments unfold on their own and you'll get what you want.
AQUARIUS. (Jan. 20 - Feb. 17): You are entering one of the richest chapters of your life â€“ both financially and metaphorically.
PISCES. (Feb. 18 - March 19): You may think that you need to be somewhere else, but the Stars show that you're right where you should be for unlocking that inner potential that will transform your life.
